artists.biography: John Shuttleworth is a comedy character played by actor Graham Fellows. Shuttleworth is a retired gentleman, living in Sheffield, South Yorkshire, England. He composes tunes of profound philosophical importance (though he has been known, on occasion, to get "a little bit blue"). and performs them at the local sheltered accomodation. Shuttleworth has appeared in several radio and television series, as well as regularly performing live. Fellows has also performed as Jilted John. Read more on Last.fm.
